ZH: 他仰望着星空。
EN: He looked up at the stars.

ZH: 她仰视着那位名人。
EN: She looks up to that celebrity.

ZH: 我们要仰赖你的帮助。
EN: We have to rely on your help.

ZH: 他仰身朝后倒。
EN: He threw himself back.

ZH: 孩子们仰望着一大群彩色气球。
EN: The children gazed up at a bunch of colorful balloons.

ZH: 奶奶仰赖着拐杖行走。
EN: Grandma relies on a cane to walk.

ZH: 他仰赖着瑜伽来放松自己。
EN: He relies on yoga to relax.

ZH: 老板仰赖这家公司的工作人员。
EN: The boss relies on the employees of this company.

ZH: 我仰慕他的勇气。
EN: I admire his courage.

ZH: 她仰慕着那幅名画。
EN: She admires that famous painting.

ZH: 他仰仰开口，却说不出话来。
EN: He opened his mouth to speak but couldn't say anything.

ZH: 她仰幕的拒绝让他尴尬不已。
EN: Her blunt rejection made him feel embarrassed.

ZH: 公司仰了他好几年，却因为一次失误而解雇他。
EN: The company supported him for several years but fired him for one mistake.

ZH: 这部电影仰赖了大量特效制作。
EN: This movie relied heavily on special effects.

ZH: 老板仰赖这名员工处理重要事务。
EN: The boss relies on this employee to handle important matters.

ZH: 他的成功仰赖于他的努力和毅力。
EN: His success depends on his hard work and perseverance.

ZH: 这个计划的成功仰赖于每个团队成员的配合。
EN: The success of this project depends on the cooperation of each team member.

ZH: 她仰赖音乐来减轻压力。
EN: She relies on music to relieve stress.

ZH: 他每天早晨仰仰着一杯咖啡。
EN: He starts his day off with a cup of coffee every morning.

ZH: 我们应该仰赖独立思考，而不是盲目跟从。
EN: We should rely on independent thinking rather than blindly following others.
